@char Nanoka.OptionB_Body1,Angry,ArmL4,ArmR1 pos:50,50 scale:1.0 !Lazy
@voice "Hewkick_complement1_5_main_021"
Nanoka: （那么一个小房间？水精之室里有什么？）
