@char Ema.ArmR1,ArmL1,Default pos:70,50 scale:1.0 !Lazy
第二天早上，樱羽艾玛果然出现了。

@char Nanoka.ArmL1,ArmR1,Normal1 pos:-50,50 scale:1.0 !Lazy
@char Ema.ArmR1,ArmL1,Surprised pos:70,50 scale:1.0 !Lazy
@char Nanoka.ArmL1,ArmR1,Normal1 pos:30,50 scale:1.0 time:0.5 !Lazy
虽然看起来有些迟疑，<br>但她还是告诉了我水精之室下方的密室。
@char Ema.ArmR1,ArmL1,Pensive pos:70,50 scale:1.0 !Lazy
@char Nanoka.ArmL1,ArmR1,Normal1 pos:30,50 scale:1.0 !Lazy
@char Ema.ArmL1,Smile,ArmR8 pos:70,50 scale:1.0 !Lazy
@char Nanoka.ArmR1,Normal1,ArmL4 pos:30,50 scale:1.0 !Lazy
作为【交易】，我选择相信她，<br>并让她帮我把风。
@hideChars !Lazy
@back 31_1 Scale:{g_backgroundDefaultScale} !Lazy
@back Transparent.Custom SubId:"Overlay" dissolve:"VerticalBlindGradually" tint:"#000000" time:0.7 !Lazy
